data.description: This home is in the sweet spot of imperial Harbor, a 55 and over community, where you own the land and no HOA fees. Totally renovated with new kitchen, bathrooms and appliances you will want to stay in this beautiful and peaceful place. Best location in this neighborhood with a preserve on the back of the house. There is an optional club membership you can purchase for $1,500 and after is only $350 yearly to maintain, that gives you access to amenities like swimming pool, fitness center, shuffle board courts and much more. A great retirement home or a fantastic rental property. A perfect piece of paradise.
